25 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - OPERATIONS. There is hereby authorized, for
26 the Administrative Office of the Courts - Operations for the 2025-2026 fiscal
27 year, the following maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be
28 known as "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such
29 purposes: two (2) temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates of
30 pay not to exceed those provided in the Uniform Classification and
31 Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act for the appropriate
32 classification.
